Class CreatePdfFromServletThread

    • java.lang.Thread

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    INameableTask, Runnable

    public class CreatePdfFromServletThread
extends LongRunningTask
    Creation of PDF-Files as long running task for GoobiContentServerServlet. First of all the variables have to be set via the setters after that you can initialize and run it
